txt.en: You have encountered wild and corrupt Huorns of the Balewood. They must be defeated to protect the inhabitants of the forest.

You have discovered Huorns of the Balewood. In NÃºrzum's wake, they have grown wild, and a cruel chill wreathes their branches. They must be defeated for the safety of all that remain in the forest until Finglas can be roused to restore order.
You have defeated many unruly Huorns in the Balewood. None would have remained safe if the Huorns remained free to rampage through the wood.
You have defeated many Huorns of the Balewood, and in doing so, have freed the Ents from their tumultuous rampaging.
Frost-touched Huorns can be found throughout northern Balewood.\n\nYou must defeat Huorns of the Balewood to protect its inhabitants from their tumultuous rampages.
